# wifi

# Notes on getting wifi working without having to dig in to
# the nightmarish hellscape of the wpa_supplicant source
# code, or networkmanager, or any of those, because they're
# all way too goddamn complicated. Hence...

# iwd
https://iwd.wiki.kernel.org

## start here
https://iwd.wiki.kernel.org/gettingstarted

```
git clone git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/libs/ell/ell
git clone git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/network/wireless/iwd
pushd iwd
./bootstrap
./configure --prefix=/lfsfs --localstatedir=/var --sysconfdir=/etc --disable-systemd-service
```
